{"tid":1321528,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（21/7）每次睇梁天琦封公開信呢段都好感慨","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T18:26:53.000Z","uid":53736,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f28e30ea58f61b6694f3559ef43c9a48400cb904","tid":1321528,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;經過這幾年的風波，我重新學會了很多寫在紙上的道理。我要感謝所有我在路上遇見的人，特別是帶我來到世上的父母親。我想，我就算窮此一生，都不夠報答父母的恩情。但如果我能夠汲取今日的教訓，始終為下一代的未來而奮鬥，相信父母依然會為之高興。&rdquo;梁天琦&mdash;寫在判刑前<br />\n<br />\n一直諗唔明點解只有人民要因為政制既不足而負責，要犧牲自由、親情、友情入獄<br />\n而冇官員為此而負責<br />\n既然政府承認送中係錯，點解阻止錯誤發生既人民要比人判<br />\n愈諗愈唔對路 似玩弄緊香港人<br />\n21/7無論點好都保住自己<br />\n唔好比狗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到有義士比人拉救到就救<br />\n身邊仲有好多人同事等大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc12815b77762141bd2f92f2097ca7cc7dc41359","tid":1321528,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f9d2a81066e3f14db8bf34742ceef2db9e312b","tid":1321528,"uid":22482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb098c3d096b69f630ba9e8c406a8dbeafe76d3","tid":1321528,"uid":261357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f785d4c747fbdb18d97883d392ee5ee3e6aa2f","tid":1321528,"uid":22460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"覺得無力感重嘅香港人 好希望你可以入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60ba850a7459a0ea03644028f95f4f4c7438a30f","tid":1321528,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:26:53.000Z","msg"